    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Games where words have to be formed with letters. They are played for entertainment, can also be used for educational purposes. Some word games are simply played with pen and paper, others with adapted game material, and some popular television programs consist of word games.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
